{"tid":808855,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好人好事]喺巴士執到失物交去警署","createTime":"2018-09-06T16:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T00:41:35.000Z","uid":112426,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b1668149854bff60684b33473f22e6df5e35a7","tid":808855,"uid":112426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"我琴日跌左卡套係巴士，入面有好多證件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現唔見之後即刻打去城巴cs，佢幫我問站頭話冇執到，我再去報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後今朝警署打嚟話有人執到，我勁興奮即刻去攞返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來香港仲有好人好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我八卦問下係邊執到(想知係咪真係喺巴士跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，警察話係巴士另一總站(我撘嘅相反方向) ，跟住佢話執到嘅人係駕駛人士，應該係巴士司機<br />\n<br />\n但係正路唔係會交去總站站頭，佢又點揸揸下車交去中途站附近警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實警察係咪check到報案人有車牌？所以估佢係車長？恕我無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽聞交去警署好似有好多手續，有啲人話放係郵筒，但如果唔見咁重要嘅嘢一定會去報失，交去警署好似係最快搵返物主嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我真係好感激有好心人唔嫌浪費時間，肯交去警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似太長，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55ebdf4a705c8065f1fbef6a63a8b48b3539b3b","tid":808855,"uid":54566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"38610bab6caae531df7dfe5c2a6c82edfa7394d3","tid":808855,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"試過執到一疊證件<br />\n交左去報案室<br />\n都唔會搞好耐啫"},{"pid":"9a08853ed027125be088b38c5fd82bdce0176e21","tid":808855,"uid":130086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"咁快搵返d失物就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔見財物，特別係身分證，報失會提高搵返財物既機會<br />\n因為警察會係電腦系統，將lost property 同 found property 做matching<br />\n14日內，如果搵唔到物主，所有證件同卡都會寄返俾相關機構<br />\n<br />\nP.S 在證物室做"},{"pid":"45799eed4b93657390a47606f707588e2a8a2493","tid":808855,"uid":112426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38610bab6caae531df7dfe5c2a6c82edfa7394d3","tid":808855,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"試過執到一疊證件<br />\n交左去報案室<br />\n都唔會搞好耐啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  對某啲人，行去警署同等交低失物嗰段時間已經覺得好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但講到尾冇人有義務幫人交失物，希望多啲好心人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9268aa497b99bf56b1844db34d9a786e3d00fd73","tid":808855,"uid":112426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a08853ed027125be088b38c5fd82bdce0176e21","tid":808855,"uid":130086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"咁快搵返d失物就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔見財物，特別係身分證，報失會提高搵返財物既機會<br />\n因為警察會係電腦系統，將lost property 同 found property 做matching<br />\n14日內，如果搵唔到物主，所有證件同卡都會寄返俾相關機構<br />\n<br />\nP.S 在證物室做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係唔見身份證，我諗住報失可以防止啲證件俾人用又多個機會搵返，好彩match到之後咁快搵返唔使補領啲證件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de93be7c3203af22ae350465c3fb50d81754f8b5","tid":808855,"uid":41139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:35:03.000Z","msg":"香港真係需要好多好多既呢啲人"},{"pid":"65eccfecd97bf970a5a67bcef5b082bd57e75059","tid":808855,"uid":51604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"我星期日落巴士發現唔見左8達通連身份証到而家都未有消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}